title: A Joe Rogan Experience Review 180
description:
This week we review 1359 Roseanne Barr, 1360 Nikki Glaser and 1362 Lenny Clarke.

Roseanne is a legend of comedy from the 80s and recently had controversey with a tweet she made.

Nikki is a comedian with a new special out called Banging on Netflix.

Lenny is another legend of comedy from the Boston scene in the 80s. He's seen it all.

You Tube “Comic Strip Live” for some great old Lenny stand up..

Enjoy my review folks!
